data.description: Fully renovated with appliances and siding in 2018.   New roof 2015. This 4BR 2BA home offers main floor living complete with an open kitchen, dining room and living room with tons of natural lighting, 1 main floor bedroom, full bathroom, and laundry. Upper level offers 3 large bedrooms and an additional full bathroom.  This home is tucked away in a quiet area, on a dead end street (surrounded by trees and wildlife).  This property is just minutes away from bike/walking trails.  Close to downtown, shopping, restaurants and entertainment.  This home also has a large yard with fire pit and room for fun outdoor entertainment.  Listing agent is related to the seller.
